Package hrps.entity

Class OrderedRoomService

  • java.lang.Object
    • hrps.entity.OrderedRoomService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class OrderedRoomService
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class represents room service's order which contains one or many orders of menu items. Each room service order is assigned a unique ID, the room which ordered the service, the order's date time, guest's remark and order's status.
    Author:
    Peng Wenxuan
